Loach is a dish enjoyed by the Dorgeshuun cave goblins. It is a simple dish, consisting of a steamed locally-caught loach, referred to by some as a goblin fish.

Loach heal 3 hitpoints when eaten and can only be received at random when trading with gourmets in the Dorgesh-Kaan marketplace. They also give a temporary Cooking boost of +1.

Trivia[edit | edit source]

  • Its appearance is similar to that of a Blobfish.
